\lvert{x}\rvert=\sqrt{x^2}
f(x)=x\lvert{x}\rvert
f(x)=x(x^2)^\frac{1}{2}
f'(x)=\sqrt{x^2}+x\frac{1}{2}(x^2)^{-\frac{1}{2}}(2x)=\sqrt{x^2}+\frac{x^2}{\sqrt{x^2}}=\frac{2x^2}{\sqrt{x^2}} =\frac{2x^2}{\lvert{x}\rvert}=2\lvert{x}\rvert 
\lvert{x}\rvert = (x^2)^\frac{1}{2}=x^{2(\frac{1}{2})}=x
\lvert{x}\rvert=\sqrt{x^2}
\lvert{x}\rvert=x
